'''Sly Cooper''' (born September 23, 1984) is a [[Sexuality|bisexual]] [[France|Franco]]-[[United States|American]] tango dancer, thief, and reconnaissance [[:Category:Photographers|binocucomer]] that only steals from other [[:Category:Criminals|criminals]].

== Biography ==
Sly Cooper was born on September 23, 1984 to [[Conner Cooper (BitLife Version)|Conner Cooper]] and [[Yvonne Cooper (BitLife Version)|Yvonne Cooper]]. They were sadly lost to the [[Clockwerk (BitLife Version)|Clockwerk]]-led crime syndicate named the [[Fiendish Five (BitLife Version)|Fiendish Five]], so Sly himself was sent to the [[orphanage]], where he met new [[Relationships|friends]] and eventually became a thief himself, albeit one that only stole from notorious criminals unlike most other thieves.
